data.description:
$5000 towards closing costs, rate buy down or even towards the purchase
price!! Welcome to this well-maintained home on 1 acre. When you enter, you'll find a bright and airy interior with an open floor plan that is great for entertaining. You'll love the fully equipped kitchen with large island, stainless appliances, low maintenance custom epoxy counters and large dining area. All flooring has recently been upgraded with tile and vinyl plank so no carpet to vacuum! Step onto the specious deck to enjoy a barbecue or have a swim in the pool. If you're an animal lover, you will appreciate the chicken coop! And there is plenty of room for a garden. One of the storage containers will remain so plenty of space for your toys and yard tools.  Property is fully fenced for your pets with a remote gate for your convenience!
